node.text: I love the versatility of @victoriabeckhambeauty’s Satin Kajal Liner in Ash. I’ve typically been a Cocoa fan but Ash is a little fresher, more modern. I use it in my lash line and waterline for subtle definition, but it can be winged or smudged for a more dramatic, day-to-night look. x VB
